---
import { BarChart3, RefreshCw, Smartphone, ShieldCheck, Zap, TrendingUp, CheckCircle2 } from 'lucide-react';
---

<div class="my-20 p-8 sm:p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-950/50 via-purple-950/30 to-black border-2 border-indigo-500/40 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-12 translate-x-12 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 border border-indigo-500/40 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-300">
        <RefreshCw class="w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-spin" />
        <span>Unikalna Wartość • Live API Sync</span>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter text-white leading-tight">
        Panel Klienta 24/7. <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400">
          Wyniki w czasie rzeczywistym.
        </span>
      </h3>

      <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-medium">
        Koniec z czekaniem na statyczne PDF-y pod koniec miesiąca. Każdy nasz klient otrzymuje dostęp do **Panelu Klienta Foundly**, połączonego bezpośrednio przez oficjalne API z **Google Analytics 4, Google Ads oraz Meta Ads**.
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-3 pt-2">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white/80">
          <CheckCircle2 class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-400 shrink-0" />
          <span>Automatyczna aktualizacja danych codziennie o północy</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white/80">
          <CheckCircle2 class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-400 shrink-0" />
          <span>Proste wskaźniki: liczba telefonów, formularzy i koszt pozyskania leada (CPL)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-white/80">
          <CheckCircle2 class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-400 shrink-0" />
          <span>Podgląd pozycji w Google Maps oraz zwrotu z inwestycji (ROAS)</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    {/* Makietowy Podgląd Panelu Live */}
    <div class="lg:col-span-6">
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[#080811] border border-indigo-500/30 shadow-2xl relative space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></div>
            <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-white">Panel Klienta • Live Status</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-indigo-400 bg-indigo-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border border-indigo-500/20">
            API Connected: GA4 + Ads
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/40 uppercase mb-1">Pozyskane Leady (Ten msc)</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white italic">48 <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400 font-normal">↑ +24%</span></div>
            <div class="text-[9px] text-white/30 mt-1">Telefony + Formularze</div>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/40 uppercase mb-1">Średni Koszt Leada (CPL)</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-black text-indigo-400 italic">28,50 zł</div>
            <div class="text-[9px] text-white/30 mt-1">Google & Meta Ads</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase mb-3">
            <span>Pozycja w Google (Frazy Lokalne)</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-400 font-mono">TOP 3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-white/10 h-2 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 h-full w-[85%]"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
